<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 01:56:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>疫情放缓后，全球绿色转型正在重振中国对非洲的投资</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252032/global-green-transition-re-energising-chinas-investments-africa-after-pandemic-slowdown?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>对可再生能源至关重要的矿产的争夺推动了中国在非洲的投资和建设交易的增加。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 01:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252032/global-green-transition-re-energising-chinas-investments-africa-after-pandemic-slowdown?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过三项涉及中国人权、亚太合作的法案</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252124/us-house-passes-three-bills-china-human-rights-asia-pacific-cooperation?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>其中一项立法授权采取进一步行动保护维吾尔族人口，而另一项立法将有助于反击北京有关西藏的虚假信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 22:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252124/us-house-passes-three-bills-china-human-rights-asia-pacific-cooperation?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>帕劳总统威胁称，如果美国资金进一步推迟，帕劳将转向北京</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252122/palaus-president-raises-threat-pivot-beijing-if-us-funds-are-delayed-further?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>总统小苏兰吉尔·惠普斯 (Surangel Whipps Jnr) 在给美国参议员的信中写道，当地领导人希望“以牺牲台湾为代价，以改变联盟为代价”从北京获得更多财政援助。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 22:13:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252122/palaus-president-raises-threat-pivot-beijing-if-us-funds-are-delayed-further?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着中国人争先恐后地存钱，“每个人都意识到冬天已经到来”，他们正在努力摆脱寒冷</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252090/chinese-scramble-save-money-everyone-realises-winter-has-come-and-theyre-trying-get-out-cold?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国房地产和股市保证收益的日子已经一去不复返了，导致中产阶级投资者凭借辛苦赚来的储蓄和家庭财富变得更加规避风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 22:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252090/chinese-scramble-save-money-everyone-realises-winter-has-come-and-theyre-trying-get-out-cold?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>全球南方表明已准备好挑战美国领导的不公平世界秩序</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/world/article/3252000/global-south-shows-its-ready-challenge-unfair-us-led-world-order?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>最近呼吁全球治理改革的 G77 峰会以及南非国际法院针对以色列的种族灭绝案，突显了发展中国家对以西方为中心的全球秩序的厌恶并愿意采取行动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 21:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/world/article/3252000/global-south-shows-its-ready-challenge-unfair-us-led-world-order?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟贸易组织长期负责人离开中国表示投资者仍然热衷，但持更多保留态度</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252119/leaving-china-long-time-eu-trade-group-chief-says-investors-remain-keen-more-reservations?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国欧盟商会名誉会长伍特克表示，跨国公司仍然希望投资，但障碍包括制造业产能过剩和高层领导缺乏坦诚。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 18:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252119/leaving-china-long-time-eu-trade-group-chief-says-investors-remain-keen-more-reservations?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>“涉及中国游客的事故”后，中国警告在巴厘岛度假的国民注意安全风险</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252110/china-warns-nationals-holidaying-bali-mind-safety-risks-after-accidents-involving-chinese-tourists?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>驻登巴萨总领馆在微信帖子中提醒中国公民不要骑无证滑板车，并注意山路和水中的风险，但数小时内删除了有关致命事故的内容。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 14:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252110/china-warns-nationals-holidaying-bali-mind-safety-risks-after-accidents-involving-chinese-tourists?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国正在向欧洲和亚洲开放免签规则。为什么日本和英国没有晋级？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251442/china-opening-visa-free-rules-europe-and-asia-why-have-japan-and-uk-not-made-cut?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>观察人士表示，将经济强国日本和英国排除在外，表明中国在寻求提振后疫情时代经济的同时，仍然注重地缘政治考虑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3251442/china-opening-visa-free-rules-europe-and-asia-why-have-japan-and-uk-not-made-cut?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>春节旅游高峰期间，前往热门海岛度假胜地海南的中国游客遭遇返程机票短缺</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252098/chinese-tourists-visiting-popular-island-resort-hainan-caught-out-return-ticket-shortages-amid-lunar?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>由于一时兴起前往这个热带岛屿的旅客发现自己因缺票而陷入困境，航空当局希望增加航班。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:53:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252098/chinese-tourists-visiting-popular-island-resort-hainan-caught-out-return-ticket-shortages-amid-lunar?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>与美国不同，中国股市无需担心特朗普当选总统</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/united-states/article/3252018/chinas-stock-market-has-little-fear-trump-presidency-unlike-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>尽管唐纳德·特朗普将中国股市的下跌归功，但事实是，中国的国内因素而非外部因素在发挥作用。相反，重点应该放在特朗普连任后对美国民主、法治和美国经济政策可信度的威胁上。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 11:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/united-states/article/3252018/chinas-stock-market-has-little-fear-trump-presidency-unlike-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国王毅将在慕尼黑安全会议上倡导“平等有序的多极世界”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252075/chinas-wang-yi-champion-equal-and-orderly-multipolar-world-munich-security-conference?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>最高外交官王毅将参加在德国举行的被称为“国防达沃斯”的年度会议，该会议可能会讨论中东和乌克兰的战争问题。在欧洲期间，中国外长还将访问西班牙和法国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 10:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252075/chinas-wang-yi-champion-equal-and-orderly-multipolar-world-munich-security-conference?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为遏制农历新年经济低迷，上海雇佣飞机、火车和汽车接工人回家</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252079/shanghai-hires-planes-trains-and-automobiles-bring-workers-back-and-curb-lunar-new-year-lull?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>为期一周的假期使得维持生产水平变得更加困难，因为各省市正面临着加速中国经济引擎的压力，加剧了对劳动力资源的竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252079/shanghai-hires-planes-trains-and-automobiles-bring-workers-back-and-curb-lunar-new-year-lull?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>Rokid 首席执行官表示，苹果的 Vision Pro 引发了人们对扩展现实技术的兴趣，刺激了对更实惠的耳机的更广泛需求</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252013/apples-vision-pro-raises-interest-extended-reality-technology-spurring-broader-demand-more?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>Rokid首席执行官Misa Zhu Mingming表示，苹果的Vision Pro耳机预计将刺激对更实惠且符合人体工程学设计的AR和VR可穿戴设备的更广泛需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252013/apples-vision-pro-raises-interest-extended-reality-technology-spurring-broader-demand-more?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国团队测试肺部治疗方法，这可能是第一个扭转影响7亿人的慢性疾病损害的方法</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3252047/chinese-team-tests-lung-treatment-may-be-first-reverse-damage-chronic-disease-affecting-700-million?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>该论文遵循左伟的说法，“基于干细胞和祖细胞的再生医学可能是治愈慢性阻塞性肺病的最大希望，即使不是唯一希望”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 07:15:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3252047/chinese-team-tests-lung-treatment-may-be-first-reverse-damage-chronic-disease-affecting-700-million?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中澳关系：一旦北京取消进口关税，Treasury Wine 准备运送奔富 (Penfolds) 和 Icon 酒瓶</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252025/china-australia-relations-treasury-wine-readies-ship-penfolds-icon-bottles-once-beijing-lifts-import?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国正在审查对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税，人们普遍预期下个月将取消关税，富邑葡萄酒庄园计划从其他全球市场重新分配库存。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 05:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252025/china-australia-relations-treasury-wine-readies-ship-penfolds-icon-bottles-once-beijing-lifts-import?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>